  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safety and effectivess of a single
      intramuscular injection of peramivir for the treatment of subjects with acute, uncomplicated
      influenza.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
